{"id": "ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ", "rating": 4.1, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 183, "displayName": {"text": "Punjabi Dhaba - Berkeley", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oYVEybElTRFoxUkdKRlRVbHFlRGgyTVZwWE5XYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Love the food at this place. Try the samosa chat that topped w chutneys and Chana masala. The chai is one of the best in town (a relief from terrible cafe chai). The seating is minimal but super clean and good music.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Love the food at this place. Try the samosa chat that topped w chutneys and Chana masala. The chai is one of the best in town (a relief from terrible cafe chai). The seating is minimal but super clean and good music.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Claudia E", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102428517820543136914/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXKhHjGZjVODVbkvtTnz_mEU7xeKqUDdbJLmuxNJqOsgbemFAK=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T19:29:41.343990897Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oYVEybElTRFoxUkdKRlRVbHFlRGgyTVZwWE5XYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25oYVEybElTRFoxUkdKRlRVbHFlRGgyTVZwWE5XYxAB!2m1!1s0x80857dc61b9dba8b:0xf4be206d96bacc6b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wQ2NuZDZZbTkzYkhKS1RWcHJUMDUzV21oeVVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "Ordered butter chicken with rice which was over $16 and it only came with THREE SMALL pieces of chicken. Overly filled with butter sauce to make it look full even though it only had three pieces of chicken. Too BURNING hot to eat as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ordered butter chicken with rice which was over $16 and it only came with THREE SMALL pieces of chicken. Overly filled with butter sauce to make it look full even though it only had three pieces of chicken. Too BURNING hot to eat as well.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "hobiprints", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105145590716499896984/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhlNpWPQKK9p1n7Y8ZlgWODtEyUpnB2iG8XQNYp9WsP9qLU_iG=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-06T04:59:26.405510827Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wQ2NuZDZZbTkzYkhKS1RWcHJUMDUzV21oeVVsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25wQ2NuZDZZbTkzYkhKS1RWcHJUMDUzV21oeVVsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857dc61b9dba8b:0xf4be206d96bacc6b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURvcklqSWZREAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "ordered through UberEats, so no clue on the atmosphere or in restaurant service. 1st off, the Lassi i ordered was missing from my delivery. Don't know if it was missing from the restaurant or a mess up by ubereats driver.\nPavbhaji was amazing! very flavorful and perfect portion.\nChicken Naan was a bit too doughy and had very little flavor.\nwill try this place in restaurant.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "ordered through UberEats, so no clue on the atmosphere or in restaurant service. 1st off, the Lassi i ordered was missing from my delivery. Don't know if it was missing from the restaurant or a mess up by ubereats driver.\nPavbhaji was amazing! very flavorful and perfect portion.\nChicken Naan was a bit too doughy and had very little flavor.\nwill try this place in restaurant.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Rajesh Kariya", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/107644796770257373373/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEFZgmppZq0LwmKVpjUQ97js4xNuBNCm139O3O96IiypjMFQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-04-22T14:30:47.068627Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURvcklqSWZREAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURvcklqSWZREAE!2m1!1s0x80857dc61b9dba8b:0xf4be206d96bacc6b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aRFJqVTRPVzFyVTFOb09UaEtPV1ZhZVRWdmRFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "Visited on: October 4, 2025\n\nI visited Punjabi Dhaba – Berkeley recently. The place is neat and clean, and overall it gives a good impression when you walk in.\n\nBefore ordering, I asked the cashier whether the biryani or roti and curry were better. He said both are good, so I ordered the goat biryani. Unfortunately, it was terrible — it had carrots and green peas in it, which really don’t belong in goat biryani. It tasted like mixed goat curry and rice rather than real biryani.\n\nHowever, the garlic naan and malai kofta curry were excellent, and the pav bhaji was also very tasty. Those dishes definitely made up for the disappointment with the biryani.\n\nMy suggestion to the staff: please be honest when recommending dishes. Customers come in wanting to enjoy good food — it’s better to guide them toward your best and most popular items rather than saying everything is great. Selling one bad dish can lose a returning customer.\n\nOverall, it’s a good place for rotis, naans, and curries — but avoid the biryani, it’s not authentic at all (just curry mixed with rice).", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Visited on: October 4, 2025\n\nI visited Punjabi Dhaba – Berkeley recently. The place is neat and clean, and overall it gives a good impression when you walk in.\n\nBefore ordering, I asked the cashier whether the biryani or roti and curry were better. He said both are good, so I ordered the goat biryani. Unfortunately, it was terrible — it had carrots and green peas in it, which really don’t belong in goat biryani. It tasted like mixed goat curry and rice rather than real biryani.\n\nHowever, the garlic naan and malai kofta curry were excellent, and the pav bhaji was also very tasty. Those dishes definitely made up for the disappointment with the biryani.\n\nMy suggestion to the staff: please be honest when recommending dishes. Customers come in wanting to enjoy good food — it’s better to guide them toward your best and most popular items rather than saying everything is great. Selling one bad dish can lose a returning customer.\n\nOverall, it’s a good place for rotis, naans, and curries — but avoid the biryani, it’s not authentic at all (just curry mixed with rice).", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "abhishek reddy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105221094871978132830/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-TQ4k05A32nE2IBNkW3RkET-4o3BKTM71mbkBt6-6kbgOaOM=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-13T00:14:12.356515121Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aRFJqVTRPVzFyVTFOb09UaEtPV1ZhZVRWdmRFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21aRFJqVTRPVzFyVTFOb09UaEtPV1ZhZVRWdmRFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857dc61b9dba8b:0xf4be206d96bacc6b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25rMWNXNXpTakpQUVV3emNVY3dWa2c1ZWsxdVYwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Made a quick stop to try their egg biryani and to be honest I came for the chicken one but I never had tried or even heard of egg biryani before so I went with that and I must say it was a good choice especially if your a vegetarian who want the taste of biryani, but without meat, so if you’re ever in the area and are craving biryani you know where to go now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Made a quick stop to try their egg biryani and to be honest I came for the chicken one but I never had tried or even heard of egg biryani before so I went with that and I must say it was a good choice especially if your a vegetarian who want the taste of biryani, but without meat, so if you’re ever in the area and are craving biryani you know where to go now.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Hashim", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113081283218750232727/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1daGnT7FrkGJKbsETykrIwcdtpYvXnmWmFCkToZ6qUqO4og=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2025-12-30T08:55:04.167978228Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25rMWNXNXpTakpQUVV3emNVY3dWa2c1ZWsxdVYwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25rMWNXNXpTakpQUVV3emNVY3dWa2c1ZWsxdVYwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80857dc61b9dba8b:0xf4be206d96bacc6b"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJi7qdG8Z9hYARa8y6lm0gvvQ/photos/AWCwydgLg61JjauupDUicxnnlMsGihgn26cDmMUeUub7_C_qJVL-wat-37CIPKEI7NocCTdyVGlx2eyuXw6brIeiHFiYz1vK7vPAlvwodTfsDts0tiRPQtGLQXVUlETsOkpipDgtkmy6SkFjU-tX-FpUFJx5q2x7HJxCkRPr2zui8bVjZE6AvTtqWwTA_v9HGT132fdifr6-Zje9KwIgAjZFhLcW4Mh7gl_OakrXXCI0f69_5_DqVdJJ13DROSzRKSQGwVQLaYkKC1z2mdgjmpebbmG0tzsYguaA1z2LJhEKz9z8EtO5sIDHC7399nOlFazf9PQcd9evQzQnOrkhlcOn6QN7VrrgYGVBp9nBwrTCo7Gg-1a9Nm0Mf8DCXLZn1NWOfr9Q9bIUp2RldATXGajl1pWFFF1fCP40rHYJpYLRKpZ-vg", "widthPx": 3024, "heightPx": 4032, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Punjabi Dhaba - Be